      "skills": "Learners will be able to: (1) classify pairs of events as mutually exclusive or not mutually exclusive using sorting activities and Venn diagrams; (2) calculate P(A ∪ B) for mutually exclusive events; (3) communicate reasoning about event classification using precise mathematical language.",
      "attitudes": "Learners will appreciate that careful mathematical classification of outcomes helps reduce guesswork in everyday decisions — just as Mama Njeri can use probability to make smarter stocking decisions at her mandazi stall.",
